Blockbuster Inc., the bankrupt
movie-rental company, won court permission for an amended loan
to fund operations in bankruptcy, after changing terms for
lenders and milestones the company must meet as it reorganizes.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tiffany Kary in New York at 
